data.description: Up to $10,000.00 in concessions.  Offering a VA assumption for a qualified VA buyer at 2.875% interest.  Also offering lender incentive for non VA buyer if using the sellers preferred lender.This stunning home in New Braunfels is a true gem. Inside, you'll find gorgeous hard floors, plenty of natural light that illuminates the high ceilings and open layout, and unique design elements that give this home its character. The kitchen is an absolute dream for any home chef, with a large island, granite countertops, and high-end appliances that make cooking a breeze. The house also offers a flexible space that can be adapted to fit your needs, as well as a primary bedroom with a modern en suite bathroom and walk-in closet. There are also three additional spacious bedrooms, a three-car garage, and plenty of parking. The backyard is perfect for outdoor entertaining with its large covered patio and built-in smart screen, allowing you to comfortably enjoy the outdoors. Whether you're hosting a barbecue or simply relaxing on a sunny day, this home is the perfect place to do it. Don't wait, make this beautiful home yours today!
